snippet.title: Zagger
snippet.description:
Game Link: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.iconic.zagger&hl=en

This is a super fun / difficult / Challenging game, where you need to check your accuracy of angles and eye to finger movement.

Collect diamonds and keep the ball on the floor.

Points will rise as long as you play.

And not to forget a very soothing environment.

Cheers
